headline: GTA Online
subtitle: ARMS IN ARMS
content:
Calling All Gunrunners: Running low on supplies? New Resupply Missions are now available to help keep your subterranean fortress fully stocked.

Want to boost research in your Bunker? Call Agent 14. Looking to expand your trade network? He can secure a contract with Ammu-Nation so you can sell your excess weapon parts for cash and spread your firepower throughout San Andreas.
